show.title: Hidden Dragon-The Little Security Guard
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/hFUqtu
show.description: A wealthy tycoon hides his true identity and joins the office where his love interest works, posing as a bodyguard to find someone who loves him for who he is not for his money. At the office, he handles the challenges she faces, defeats her enemies, and eventually reveals to everyone that he is, in fact, a billionaire.
